OL,3,CSergio Perez loses Red Bull seat after
OL,4,Cdisappointing 2024 campaign
OL,6,FSergio Perez has lost his seat at Red
OL,7,FBull after a disappointing season
OL,8,Fwhere he finished 285 points behind
OL,9,Fhis teammate Max Verstappen.
OL,11,FVerstappen clinched his fourth
OL,12,Fconsecutive drivers' world title while
OL,13,FPerez, 34, finished eighth in the
OL,14,Fstandings, failing to finish in the
OL,15,Ftop five in his final 18 races for the
OL,16,Fteam.
