OL,3,CSergio Perez loses Red Bull seat after
OL,4,Cdisappointing 2024 campaign
OL,6,FPerez said: "I'm incredibly grateful
OL,7,Ffor the past four years with Oracle
OL,8,FRed Bull Racing and for the
OL,9,Fopportunity to race with such an
OL,10,Famazing team.
OL,12,F"Driving for Red Bull has been an
OL,13,Funforgettable experience and I'll
OL,14,Falways cherish the successes we
OL,15,Fachieved together.
OL,17,F"We broke records, reached remarkable
OL,18,Fmilestones and I've had the privilege
OL,19,Fof meeting so many incredible people
OL,20,Falong the way.
