OL,3,CSergio Perez loses Red Bull seat after
OL,4,Cdisappointing 2024 campaign
OL,6,FHe told the Formula 1 website in
OL,7,FSeptember he had struggled due to the
OL,8,Fdirection the team had taken with the
OL,9,Fcar.
OL,11,FPerez said Verstappen had adapted to
OL,12,Fnew changes better than he had.
OL,14,FHe said: "Some people don't understand
OL,15,Fit, especially from the media side,
OL,16,Fthat different driver styles can come
OL,17,Fto different conclusions. The problem
OL,18,Fwas... Well, not the problem ` the
OL,19,Fgood thing was that Max was less
OL,20,Fsensitive to it than I was."
