OL,3,CSergio Perez loses Red Bull seat after
OL,4,Cdisappointing 2024 campaign
OL,6,FTeam principal Christian Horner made
OL,7,Fno secret of the fact that Red Bull
OL,8,Fneeded more from Perez amid his
OL,9,Fstruggles which ultimately cost the
OL,10,FMilton-Keynes-based team the
OL,11,Fconstructors' title.
OL,13,FBut Perez played his part in the team
OL,14,Fwinning the title in 2022 and 2023 and
OL,15,Falso famously helped Verstappen during
OL,16,Fhis Abu Dhabi battle with Lewis
OL,17,FHamilton in 2021.
