OL,6,FHorner praised the Mexican's role
OL,7,Fwithin the team, saying: I would like
OL,8,Fto thank Checo for all he has done for
OL,9,FOracle Red Bull Racing over the past
OL,10,Ffour seasons."
OL,12,F"From the moment he joined in 2021, he
OL,13,Fproved himself to be an extraordinary
OL,14,Fteam player, helping us to two
OL,15,Fconstructors' titles and to our first
OL,16,F1-2 finish in the drivers'
OL,17,Fchampionship.
